    @Mojo(name="generate",
      defaultPhase=PACKAGE,
      requiresDependencyResolution=RUNTIME,
      threadSafe=true)
public class GenerateMojo
extends BaseMojo
    Generates an application file. Merges dependency jars into a single file, prepended with a launch shell script.
